    <scm>
        <connection>scm:git:git@github.com/masterthought/test-agent-framework.git</connection>
        <developerConnection>scm:git:git@github.com/masterthought/test-agent-framework.git
        </developerConnection>
        <url>git@github.com/masterthought/test-agent-framework.git</url>
    </scm>

    <description>
        This project provides a structured way of creating automation frameworks based on Agents who perform Missions.
        Agents come with a powerful Memory which can store any type of data, stored in any type of Categories or keys.
        Agency comes into picture to fork different agents and join their knowledge together.
    </description>

